{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\cf1\lang9\f0\fs28 (* )\cf2  Ch\'e8o\cf1 : lo\u7841?i k\u7883?ch h\'e1t, m\'faa d\'e2n gian, k\u7875? chuy\u7879?n, di\u7877?n t\'edch b\u7857?ng h\'ecnh th\u7913?c s\'e2u kh\u7845?uv\'e0 tr\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7899?c kia th\'fd\u7901?ng \'f0\'fd\u7907?c di\u7877?n \u7903? s\'e2n \'f0\lang1033\f0\'ecnh n\'ean c\'f2n \f2\'f0\u432?\u7907?c g\u7885?i l\f0\'e0 ch\'e8o s\'e2n \f2\'f0\f0\'ecnh. Ch\'e8o \f2\'f0\u432?\u7907?c n\f0\'e3y sinh v\'e0 ph\u7893? bi\u7871?n r\u7897?ng r\'e3i \u7903? B\u7855?c B\u7897?. \par
\lang9 T\'edch truy\u7879?n trong ch\'e8o \f2\'f0\u432?\u7907?c khai th\'e1c t\u7915? truy\u7879?n c\u7893? t\'edch v\f0\'e0 truy\u7879?n N\'f4m (Quan \'c2m Th\u7883? K\'ednh, T\u7915? Th\u7913?c, Tr\lang1066\f1\'fd\'f5ng Vi\'ean, Kim Nham, T\u7889?ng Tr\'e2n \endash  C\'fac Hoa\'85) xoay quanh tr\u7909?c b\u297? c\u7921?c (\'f0au kh\u7893?, oan tr\'e1i) \endash  th\'e1i lai (t\u7889?t \'f0\u7865?p, y\'eau vui). Ch\'e8o ch\'fa \lang1033\f0\'fd gi\u7899?i thi\u7879?u nh\u7919?ng m\u7851?u m\u7921?c v\u7873? \f2\'f0\u7841?o \'f0\u7913?c, t\f0\'e0i n\f2\'e3ng \'f0\u7875? m\u7885?i ng\u432?\u7901?i noi theo. B\f0\'can c\u7841?nh vi\u7879?c c\u7843?m th\'f4ng v\u7899?i s\u7889? ph\u7853?n bi k\u7883?ch c\u7911?a ng\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7901?i lao \'f0\u7897?ng, ng\'fd\u7901?i ph\u7909? n\u7919?, \'f0\u7873? cao ph\u7849?m ch\u7845?t v\'e0 t\'e0i n\'e3ng c\u7911?a h\u7885?, ch\'e8o c\lang1033\f0\'f2n ch\'e2m bi\u7871?m, \f2\'f0\u7843? k\'edch tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p v\f0\'e0 m\u7841?nh m\u7867? nh\u7919?ng \f2\'f0i\u7873?u b\u7845?t c\'f4ng, x\u7845?u xa trong x\f0\'e3 h\u7897?i phong ki\u7871?n \f2\'f0\u432?\u417?ng th\u7901?i. \par
\lang9\f0 Ch\'e8o c\'f3 m\u7897?t s\u7889? nh\'e2n v\u7853?t truy\u7873?n th\u7889?ng v\u7899?i nh\u7919?ng \f2\'f0\u7863?c tr\u432?ng t\'ednh c\'e1ch ri\f0\'eang nh\lang1066\f1\'fd: Th\'fd sinh th\lang1033\f0\'ec nho nh\'e3, \f2\'f0i\u7873?m \'f0\u7841?m; n\u7919? ch\'ednh: \'f0\u7913?c h\u7841?nh, n\u7871?t na; n\u7919? l\u7879?ch: l\u7859?ng l\u417?, b\u7841?o d\u7841?n; m\u7909? \'e1c: t\f0\'e0n nh\u7849?n, \f2\'f0\u7897?c \'f0\u7883?a. H\u7873? ch\'e9o l\f0\'e0 nh\lang1066\f1\'fdng vai h\'e0i mang \'f0\u7871?n ti\u7871?ng c\'fd\u7901?i th\'f4ng minh, h\u7843? h\'ea v\'e0 s\'e2u sa8c1cho ng\'fd\u7901?i xem. Nh\'e2n v\u7853?t ch\'e8o khi b\'fd\u7899?c ra s\'e2n kh\u7845?u, \'f0\u7847?u ti\'ean ph\'e0i t\u7921? x\'fdng danh (x\'fdng t\'ean, h\u7885?, qu\'ea qu\'e1n, ngh\u7873? nghi\u7879?p, t\'ednh c\'e1ch), sau \'f0\'f3 m\u7899?i b\'fd\u7899?c v\'e0o di\u7877?n t\'edch. T\'ednh ch\u7845?t \'fd\u7899?c l\u7879? c\'e1ch \'f0i\u7879?u c\u7911?a s\'e2n kh\u7845?u ch\'e8o th\u7875? hi\u7879?n r\u7845?t cao qua ngh\u7879? thu\u7853?t h\'f3a trang, ngh\u7879? thu\u7853?t h\'e1t, m\'faa c\u7911?a c\'e1c nh\'e2n v\u7853?t. Ch\u7859?ng h\u7841?n, nh\'e2n v\u7853?t l\lang1033\f0\'e3o th\'ec m\u7863?c \'e1o \f2\'f0i\u7873?u, qu\u7847?n l\u7909?a b\u7841?ch, v\u7853?n \'f0\u7897?ng tr\f0\'ean s\'e2n kh\u7845?u ch\'e8o theo \f2\'f0\u432?\u7901?ng g\f0\'e3y kh\'fac v\'e0 \f2\'f0\u432?\u7901?ng tr\f0\'f2n, \f2\'f0i\u7879?u \'f0i g\u7853?t c\u7909?c, ch\'e2n l\u7843?o \'f0\u7843?o, th\u432?\u7901?ng h\'e1t \'f0i\u7879?u b\f0\'ecnh ti\u7875?u. Nh\'e2n v\u7853?t n\u7919? ch\'ednh m\u7863?c \'e1o h\u7891?ng l\u7891?ng xa \f2\'f0en, v\u7853?n \'f0\u7897?ng tr\f0\'ean s\'e2n kh\u7845?u thei g\'f3c vu\'f4ng, \f2\'f0\u432?\u7901?ng th\u7859?ng t\u432? th\u7871? ngay th\u7859?ng, \'f0\u7875? qu\u7841?t che k\'edn \'f0\'e1o, th\u432?\u7901?ng h\'e1t \'f0i\u7879?u s\u7917? b\u7857?ng. C\f0\'f2n nh\'e2n v\u7853?t s\u7917? l\u7879?ch: d\'e1n cao \u7903? th\'e1i d\lang1066\f1\'fd\'f5ng, v\u7853?n \'f0\u7897?ng theo \'f0\'fd\u7901?ng l\'fd\u7907?n song khu\u7871?ch \'f0\u7841?i qu\'e1 m\u7913?c, \'f0\u7843?o m\u7855?t nhi\u7873?u, d\'e1ng \'f0i \'fd\u7905?n \u7865?o, nhi\u7873?u chuy\u7879?n \'f0\u7897?ng \'f0\u7897?t ng\u7897?t, th\'fd\u7901?ng h\'e1t \'f0i\u7879?u c\u7845?m gi\'e1, s\u7855?p ch\u7907?t, \'85\par
