\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab} \cf2 H\u7897?i long v\'e2n\cf1 : \'fd n\'f3i thi ch\u7917? \f2\'f0\u7895? \'f0\u7841?t (long: r\u7891?ng, v\'e2n: m\'e2y, h\u7897?i: g\u7863?p; r\u7891?ng m\'e2y g\u7863?p nhau). \par
\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab} \cf2 K\u7881?\cf1  (tr\'e0ng k\u7881?) : \u7903? \f2\'f0\'e2y l\f0\'e0 gh\u7871? ki\u7875?u c\u7893?, th\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7901?ng c\'f3 ch\u7841?m kh\u7855?c h\lang1033\f0\'ecnh \f2\'f0\u7875? trang tr\'ed. \par
\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab} \cf2 C\'f4ng h\u7847?u\cf1 : t\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7899?c c\'f4ng v\'e0 t\'fd\u7899?c h\u7847?u, c\'f4ng h\u7847?u ch\lang1033\f0\'ec chung c\'e1c ch\u7913?c t\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7899?c cao trong tri\u7873?u \'f0\lang1033\f0\'ecnh phong ki\u7871?n. \par
\cf2\lang9{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Ph\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7907?ng\cf1  (chim ph\'fd\u7907?ng ho\'e0ng) : chim t\'fd\u7903?ng t\'fd\u7907?ng ra, c\'f3 h\lang1033\f0\'ecnh th\'f9 nh\lang1066\f1\'fd chim tr\u297? v\'e0 \'f0\'fd\u7907?c xem l\'e0 ch\'faa c\u7911?a; c\'f4ng; chim qu\lang1033\f0\'fd hi\u7871?m, b\u7897? l\'f4ng m\'e0u l\u7909?c \'e1nh th\'e9p; \f2\'f0u\'f4i con tr\u7889?ng d\f0\'e0i c\'f3 nhi\u7873?u m\'e0u s\u7855?c \f2\'f0\u7865?p, c\'f3 th\u7875? x\f0\'f2e th\u7859?ng \f2\'f0\u7913?ng v\f0\'e0 x\u7871?p theo h\'ecnh nan qu\u7841?t. Gi\u7889?ng ph\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7907?ng gi\u7889?ng c\'f4ng: ch\u7881? d\lang1033\f0\'f2ng gi\u7889?ng gi\'e0u c\'f3, cao qu\'fd. \par
\cf2\lang9{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}M\'e8o m\u7843? g\'e0 \f2\'f0\u7891?ng\cf1 : m\f0\'e8o \u7903? m\u7843?, g\'e0 \u7903? \f2\'f0\u7891?ng, ch\u7881? lo\f0\'e0i v\u7853?t hoang h\'f3a, kh\'f4ng ph\'e0i l\'e0 nh\u7919?ng lo\'e0i v\u7853?t nu\'f4i trong nh\'e0, th\'e0nh ng\u7919? n\'e0y d\'f9ng \f2\'f0\u7875? ch\u7881? nh\u7919?ng k\u7867? v\'f4 l\u7841?i, thi\u7871?u gi\'e1o d\u7909?c, ma m\f0\'e3nh b\u7883?p b\u7907?m. \par
\cf2{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Tr\u7879?n d\'e2u d\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7899?i B\u7897?c \cf1 (ho\u7863?c \ldblquote d\'fd\u7899?i B\u7897?c tr\'ean d\'e2u\rdblquote ) : ch\u7881? nh\u7919?ng cu\u7897?c t\lang1033\f0\'ecnh b\u7845?t ch\'ednh (nh\u7919?ng ru\u7897?ng d\'e2u \u7903? b\'e3i B\u7897?c thu\u7897?c t\u7881?nh S\lang1066\f1\'f5n \'d0\'f4ng - Trung Qu\u7889?c l\'e0 ch\u7893? ng\'e0y x\'fda trai gi\'e1 n\'fd\u7899?c Tr\u7883?nh v\'e0 n\'fd\u7899?c V\u7879? th\'fd\u7901?ng h\u7865?n h\lang1033\f0\'f2 nhau t\'ecnh t\u7921?). \par
\cf2\lang9{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}B\u7845?t tr\u7855?c\cf1 : vi\u7879?c x\u7845?u x\u7843?y ra kh\'f3 l\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7901?ng tr\'fd\u7899?c \'f0\'fd\u7907?c. \u7902? \'f0\'e2y ch\u7881? t\'ednh d\u7889?i tr\'e1, ph\u7843?n ph\'fac. \par
\cf2\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Tam t\'f2ng t\u7913? \f2\'f0\u7913?c\lang1033\f0  \cf1 (\lang9\f2  tam: ba; t\u7913?: b\u7889?n) : th\u7901?i phong ki\u7871?n quan ni\u7879?m ph\u7909? n\u7919? ph\u7843?i tam t\f0\'f2ng (\ldblquote t\u7841?i gia t\'f2ng ph\u7909?, xu\u7845?t gi\'e0 t\'f2ng phu, phu t\u7917? t\'f2ng t\u7917?\rdblquote , t\u7913?c l\'e0 \u7903? nh\'e0 ph\u7843?i theo (ph\u7909? thu\u7897?c) cha, l\u7845?y ch\u7891?ng ph\'e0i theo ch\u7891?ng, ch\u7891?ng ch\u7871?t th\'ec theo con trai) v\'e0 t\u7913? \f2\'f0\u7913?c (\ldblquote c\'f4ng, dung, ng\'f4n, h\u7841?nh\rdblquote , t\u7913?c nh\u7919?ng ti\f0\'eau chu\u7849?n c\u7847?n c\'f3 v\u7873? c\'f4ng vi\u7879?c, dung nhan, l\u7901?i \f2\'e3n ti\u7871?ng n\'f3i v\f0\'e0 \f2\'f0\u7913?c h\u7841?nh). \par
\cf2\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}G\lang1066\f1\'fd\'f5m tr\u7901?i b\'faa nguy\u7879?t\cf1 : ch\u7881? s\u7921? tr\u7915?ng tr\u7883? c\u7911?a \'f4ng tr\u7901?i (theo quan ni\u7879?m m\'ea t\'edn). \par
\cf2\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}B\u7891?ng B\'e1o\cf1 : t\u7913?c th\'f4n B\u7891?ng Th\lang1066\f1\'fd\u7907?ng thu\u7897?c huy\u7879?n V\u297?nh L\u7897?c (Thanh H\'f3a), m\u7897?t v\'f9ng \'f0\u7845?t v\'e3n v\u7853?t th\u7901?i x\'fda, ng\u7921?a b\u7845?t kham th\'fd\u7901?ng \'f0\'fd\u7907?c \'f0\'fda v\u7873? \'f0\'e2y \'f0\u7875? thu\u7847?n h\'f3a. \par
\cf2\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}C\u7847?u N\'f4m\cf1 : thu\u7897?c huy\u7879?n V\f2\'e3n L\'e2m (H\u432?ng Y\f0\'eau) ng\'e0y nay, c\'f3 ngh\u7873? \f2\'f0\'fac \'f0\u7891?ng. \par
\cf2\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Tr\u7913?ng r\u7891?ng l\u7841?i n\u7903? ra r\u7891?ng\cf1 : ch\u7881? d\'f2ng d\'f5i cao qu\'fd, gi\'e0u c\'f3, ti\u7871?p n\u7889?i nhau. \par
\cf2{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Lia \f2\'f0iu\cf1 : r\u7855?n nh\u7887? c\'f3 n\u7885?c \'f0\u7897?c, s\u7889?ng \u7903? ao h\u7891?, \'e3n \u7871?ch nh\'e1i; \u7903? \'f0\'e2y ch\u7881? d\f0\'f2ng gi\u7889?ng h\'e8n m\u7885?n, th\u7845?p k\'e9m. \par
\cf2{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Cao m\'f4n l\u7879?nh t\u7897?c\cf1 : ch\u7881? n\lang1066\f1\'f5i gi\'e0u c\'f3, quy\u7873?n th\u7871?. \par
\cf2\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}N\u7919? t\u7855?c n\u7919? c\'f4ng\cf1 : (gi\u7887?i giang, g\lang1066\f1\'fd\'f5ng m\u7851?u v\u7873?) c\'f4ng vi\u7879?c v\'e0 \'f0\u7841?o \'f0\u7913?c, theo quan ni\u7879?m x\'fda \'f0\u7889?i v\u7899?i ng\'fd\u7901?i ph\u7909? n\u7919?. \par
\cf2\lang9\f0{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}S\u7855?t c\u7847?m t\u7883?nh h\u7843?o\cf1 : \'fd n\'f3i t\'ecnh v\u7907? ch\u7891?ng h\'f2a h\u7907?p (s\u7855?t, c\u7847?m l\'e0 hai th\u7913? \f2\'f0\f0\'e0n c\u7893?). \par
